        "subject": "LU-3471 osc: use mutex for cl_loi_list_lock instead of spinlock",
        "message": "LU-3471 osc: use mutex for cl_loi_list_lock instead of spinlock\n\nAsync page operations are not guaranteed to not block, therefore\nspinlock is not appropriate for protecting structures accessed by\nthem.\nThis patch changes the spinlock with mutex.\n\nSigned-off-by: Vladimir Saveliev <vladimir_saveliev@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: Ia54af9c3db6f5977febc7a229986c78b13ce43fc\n"
      },
